{"tid":1566711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣布 中秋已經完咗 所有慶祝活動[暫緩]","createTime":"2019-09-13T17:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T03:33:13.000Z","uid":178881,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"26697a9b936f7301babc407a449686d38b4c14c8","tid":1566711,"uid":178881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:05:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暫緩到幾時啊？<br />\n緩到佢老母<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></strong>過撚哂！<br />\n相約煲底先再慶祝！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位手足：<br />\n講好咗要「和勇共存」，就唔好得個講字。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/52uuD0p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F52uuD0p.jpg&h=3b4238a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天琦咁講係認同每一種抗爭方式，而唔係相互嘅指罵。<br />\n<br />\n既然中秋已過，而聽日就已經係週末，<br />\n我哋就要證明俾政府睇：「我哋抖夠喇！！！」<br />\n<br />\n接下來，星期六有以下活動：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RyERSno.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRyERSno.jpg&h=e9e1bceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期日有以下活動：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iaP6GfC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiaP6GfC.jpg&h=acf93dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aK6g3uG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaK6g3uG.jpg&h=867b9085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港，要人啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係時候打返主線喇！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"2b93bd5013e30f06c47e1eab1729ebd07dd2becc","tid":1566711,"uid":9846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:05:58.000Z","msg":"星期六天水圍、機場取消哂？"},{"pid":"ec447bc64890600a262bf31e23d08c03f5d3c5a1","tid":1566711,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:09:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: r